<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 12:13:33 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列北部的父母被迫在孩子的安全和教育之间做出选择</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/parents-in-northern-israel-forced-to-choose-between-childrens-safety-and-education/00000191-aa21-d2ec-a1f7-ef7178810000</link><description>在黎巴嫩近十一个月的持续轰炸中，政府未能找到解决受到威胁的道路和保护不足的教室的解决方案</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 12:06:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/parents-in-northern-israel-forced-to-choose-between-childrens-safety-and-education/00000191-aa21-d2ec-a1f7-ef7178810000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡最终谴责以色列人质在加沙的死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-has-finally-condemned-the-israeli-hostages-to-their-deaths-in-gaza/00000191-ad36-d4e9-a199-ad771b570000</link><description>出于政治考虑和军事压力而放弃被囚禁的以色列人，巩固了总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡作为独裁者的遗产，他显然对自己的公民没有任何责任感</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 11:56:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-has-finally-condemned-the-israeli-hostages-to-their-deaths-in-gaza/00000191-ad36-d4e9-a199-ad771b570000</guid></item><item><title>在火人节上，以色列新星节的“天使”复活</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/at-burning-man-angels-from-israels-nova-festival-come-back-to-life/00000191-ad2a-d453-ab9f-fdae2f6d0000</link><description>在内华达州沙漠举行的音乐节上，10 月 7 日加沙边境附近狂欢的幸存者搭建了“新星天堂”装置，向被哈马斯杀害的音乐节观众致敬</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 11:53:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/at-burning-man-angels-from-israels-nova-festival-come-back-to-life/00000191-ad2a-d453-ab9f-fdae2f6d0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡知道以色列人质的时间已经不多了。他的手上沾满了他们的血”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-knew-the-israeli-hostages-were-on-borrowed-time-their-blood-is-on-his-hands/00000191-acf1-d453-ab9f-fcfd1a3b0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡政府的一名高级成员接着说，“每个人都知道他是一个自恋者和胆小鬼”。但他的缺乏人性在最近几个月里得到了充分、丑陋的体现。</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 11:29:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-knew-the-israeli-hostages-were-on-borrowed-time-their-blood-is-on-his-hands/00000191-acf1-d453-ab9f-fcfd1a3b0000</guid></item><item><title>美国、以色列和哈马斯调解员对内塔尼亚胡总理对加沙协议的意图失去了信心</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/u-s-israel-hamas-mediators-have-lost-faith-in-netanyahu-pms-intentions-for-gaza-deal/00000191-acb5-d4e9-a199-acf502c00000</link><description>一名以色列官员补充说，内塔尼亚胡一直在停火和人质协议谈判中提出“一个又一个障碍”。以色列国防军周日从加沙打捞出六名人质尸体后，尚不清楚谈判是否会加快或一劳永逸地掩埋</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 09:20:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/u-s-israel-hamas-mediators-have-lost-faith-in-netanyahu-pms-intentions-for-gaza-deal/00000191-acb5-d4e9-a199-acf502c00000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡：那些谋杀人质的人不想达成协议；甘茨呼吁抗议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-those-who-murder-hostages-dont-want-a-deal-gantz-calls-for-protests/00000191-ac63-d172-abd9-eef72c6e0000</link><description>以色列国防军从加沙打捞出六名人质尸体后，以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡发表了一份录音声明。声明发表后，人质论坛呼吁总理对“遗弃”人质“承担责任”</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 08:33:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-those-who-murder-hostages-dont-want-a-deal-gantz-calls-for-protests/00000191-ac63-d172-abd9-eef72c6e0000</guid></item><item><title>三名以色列警察在约旦河西岸枪击事件中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/three-police-officers-killed-in-west-bank-shooting/00000191-ac42-d453-ab9f-fccee5b00000</link><description>以色列军队正在寻找在塔尔库米亚检查站附近射杀一辆载有国防人员的车辆的几名嫌疑人</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 07:07:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/three-police-officers-killed-in-west-bank-shooting/00000191-ac42-d453-ab9f-fccee5b00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队找到了最近被哈马斯处决的六名人质的尸体，这些人质被绑架到加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-recovers-bodies-of-six-hostages-kidnapped-to-gaza-by-hamas-on-october-7/00000191-abf9-d23c-a1d3-abff44100000</link><description>所有六人都被活活绑架，三人本应在与哈马斯达成协议的第一部分中被释放 ■ 以色列国防军发言人表示，他们是在拉法的一个隧道中被发现的，很可能是在部队抵达“前不久”被杀</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 06:28:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-recovers-bodies-of-six-hostages-kidnapped-to-gaza-by-hamas-on-october-7/00000191-abf9-d23c-a1d3-abff44100000</guid></item><item><title>美国总统拜登对美国裔以色列人赫什·戈德堡-波林在哈马斯囚禁期间死亡感到“震惊和愤怒”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/biden-devastated-and-outraged-over-death-of-hersh-goldberg-polin-in-hamas-captivity/00000191-abe1-dd1e-adb5-abef511c0000</link><description>戈德堡-波林的父母曾多次会见美国官员和其他国际高级领导人，并于最近在民主党全国代表大会上发表讲话。拜登说：“我对他们的钦佩和悲痛之情无法用言语表达。”</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 05:25:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/biden-devastated-and-outraged-over-death-of-hersh-goldberg-polin-in-hamas-captivity/00000191-abe1-dd1e-adb5-abef511c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军从加沙哈马斯的囚禁中打捞出六名人质的尸体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article-live/idf-finds-hostages-bodies-in-gaza-family-of-hostage-hersh-goldberg-polin-announces-death/00000191-ab89-d453-ab9f-fb8ddb250000</link><description>三名警察在约旦河西岸枪击事件中丧生 ■ 国防部长加兰特呼吁安全内阁推翻以色列继续在费城航线上驻扎的决定 ■ 美国总统对美以人质赫什·戈德堡-波林的死亡感到“震惊和愤怒” ■ 人质家庭论坛要求内塔尼亚胡公开露面，对人质死亡承担责任</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 03:36:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article-live/idf-finds-hostages-bodies-in-gaza-family-of-hostage-hersh-goldberg-polin-announces-death/00000191-ab89-d453-ab9f-fb8ddb250000</guid></item><item><title>杰宁居民称他们已被围困多日，基础设施遭到破坏</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/jenin-residents-say-theyve-been-under-siege-for-days-infrastructure-has-been-destroyed/00000191-aa36-d2ec-a1f7-ef76a4be0000</link><description>一名居民表示，停电可能会导致食物变质，居民们都呆在家里。 ■ 该市红新月会主任表示，以色列军方向救护车开枪</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 01:08:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/jenin-residents-say-theyve-been-under-siege-for-days-infrastructure-has-been-destroyed/00000191-aa36-d2ec-a1f7-ef76a4be0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军在加沙地带发现人质尸体；身份识别过程正在进行中</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/idf-finds-bodies-of-hostages-in-gaza-strip-identification-process-ongoing/00000191-aa59-d2ec-a1f7-ef79c5300000</link><description>以色列国防军宣布这一消息后，人质和失踪家庭论坛发表声明：“内塔尼亚胡已经抛弃了人质，从明天开始，国家将颤抖”</description><pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 22:42:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/idf-finds-bodies-of-hostages-in-gaza-strip-identification-process-ongoing/00000191-aa59-d2ec-a1f7-ef79c5300000</guid></item><item><title>只有以色列军事压力才能释放人质的说法始终是错误的。现在已经支离破碎了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-31/ty-article/.premium/the-claim-that-only-military-force-can-free-hostages-was-always-wrong-now-its-shattered/00000191-a9e6-d453-ab9f-f9ee87e90000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡在最近一次内阁会议上批准以色列国防军继续在费城航线驻扎，这是一个历史性的低点，即使在当前战争的历史上也是如此。现在很清楚：消灭哈马斯的斗争可能会导致更多人质丧生</description><pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 20:54:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-31/ty-article/.premium/the-claim-that-only-military-force-can-free-hostages-was-always-wrong-now-its-shattered/00000191-a9e6-d453-ab9f-f9ee87e90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在约旦河西岸杰宁与武装分子的冲突中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-31/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-killed-in-clashes-with-militants-in-jenin-west-bank/00000191-aa17-dd1e-adb5-aadf5b2a0000</link><description>交火导致参谋军士死亡。埃尔卡纳·纳冯（Elkana Navon）重伤另一名士兵，并轻伤另外两人。这些部队驻扎在杰宁，是以色列国防军周三开始在西岸行动的一部分</description><pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 20:37:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-31/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-killed-in-clashes-with-militants-in-jenin-west-bank/00000191-aa17-dd1e-adb5-aadf5b2a0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡否决了以色列国防部长的决定，决定了人质的命运</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-31/ty-article/.premium/overruling-israels-defense-chiefs-netanyahu-seals-the-hostages-fate/00000191-a9b3-d3dd-a991-a9bfe3120000</link><description>安全内阁的投票似乎是对唯一关心加沙隧道中受苦受难的人们的成员的有针对性的打击</description><pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 19:48:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-31/ty-article/.premium/overruling-israels-defense-chiefs-netanyahu-seals-the-hostages-fate/00000191-a9b3-d3dd-a991-a9bfe3120000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 330 天：以色列在约旦河西岸汽车炸弹袭击事件后逮捕了六名嫌疑人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-31/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-330-israel-arrests-six-suspects-after-west-bank-car-bomb-attacks/00000191-a941-d2ec-a1f7-ef712e5c0000</link><description>四名以色列人在西岸两起汽车炸弹袭击中受伤；两名袭击者被杀，以色列国防军逮捕了 6 名嫌疑人 ■ 以色列安全官员：爆炸物来自希伯伦的同一个实验室 ■ 以色列国防军：两名哈马斯附属武装分子在杰宁被杀 ■ 加沙卫生官员：以色列国防军的空袭造成 48 人死亡 ■ 以色列国防军：从以色列向西加利利发射了 40 枚火箭弹黎巴嫩 ■ 战争进入 330 天后您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 17:01:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-31/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-330-israel-arrests-six-suspects-after-west-bank-car-bomb-attacks/00000191-a941-d2ec-a1f7-ef712e5c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列各地数千人要求加沙达成协议，警方在特拉维夫与抗议者发生冲突</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-31/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-is-sentencing-our-loved-ones-to-death-hostages-families-demand-gaza-deal/00000191-a917-dd1e-adb5-abdf53e70000</link><description>在内塔尼亚胡内阁以人质协议为代价，批准以色列国防军继续沿费城路线驻扎后，数千人走上以色列街头。 当警察与特拉维夫的人群发生冲突时，一名人质的妹妹被一辆救护车撞伤后被疏散。骑警</description><pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 16:26:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-31/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-is-sentencing-our-loved-ones-to-death-hostages-families-demand-gaza-deal/00000191-a917-dd1e-adb5-abdf53e70000</guid></item><item><title>国际足联再次推迟对巴勒斯坦禁赛以色列请求的决定</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-08-31/ty-article/fifa-again-delays-decision-on-palestinian-request-to-suspend-israel/00000191-a90b-d172-abd9-eb9f6e8e0000</link><description>该足球机构表示，在审查法律意见后，将在 10 月份考虑这一请求，该请求引用了加沙战争并指控以色列的歧视</description><pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 15:52:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-08-31/ty-article/fifa-again-delays-decision-on-palestinian-request-to-suspend-israel/00000191-a90b-d172-abd9-eb9f6e8e0000</guid></item><item><title>预计战斗暂停前一天，加沙开始开展脊髓灰质炎疫苗接种活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-31/ty-article/.premium/polio-vaccine-campaign-begins-in-gaza-a-day-before-an-expected-pause-in-fighting/00000191-a8ce-d23c-a1d3-abefe8480000</link><description>这个为期三天的疫苗接种计划是在本月在加沙发现 25 年来首例脊髓灰质炎病例后开始的。加沙高级卫生官员表示，必须实现停火，以便救援队能够接触到此次行动中的每个目标。</description><pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 14:58:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-31/ty-article/.premium/polio-vaccine-campaign-begins-in-gaza-a-day-before-an-expected-pause-in-fighting/00000191-a8ce-d23c-a1d3-abefe8480000</guid></item><item><title>西岸汽车炸弹：以色列国防军称爆炸物来自同一希伯伦实验室，六名嫌疑人被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-31/ty-article/.premium/west-bank-car-bombs-idf-says-explosives-came-from-same-hebron-lab/00000191-a7d8-dd1e-adb5-afde7d110000</link><description>以色列国防军封锁了希伯伦，并对嫌疑人展开搜捕。当局认为恐怖组织打算发动更多袭击，并将这些事件与该地区之前发生的汽车爆炸事件联系起来</description><pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 10:19:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-31/ty-article/.premium/west-bank-car-bombs-idf-says-explosives-came-from-same-hebron-lab/00000191-a7d8-dd1e-adb5-afde7d110000</guid></item></channel></rss>